<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ع ك ك:</span> <span class="c2">(الْعُكَّةُ)</span> بِالضَّمِّ آنِيَةُ السَّمْنِ وَجَمْعُهَا <span class="c2">(عُكَكٌ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(عِكَاكٌ)</span> . وَ <span class="c2">(عَكَّةُ)</span> اسْمُ بَلَدٍ فِي الثُّغُورِ.<span class="c5"> وَفِي الْحَدِيثِ:</span> <span class="c2">«طُوبَى لِمَنْ رَأَى عَكَّةَ»</span> .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>